git status
git branch [-a]
git add
git commit [-m "commit msg"]
git push [remote_name] [branch_name]



git fetch
git pull [origin (remote branch name)]



git checkout [-b <new branch name>] [-d <onoma branch pou 8a faei delete>] [current branch name] <hash opoiodhpote commit (sto idio branch (?))>
git merge <branch name>
> git merge kai meta git checkout -d to onoma tou branch pou ekana HDH merge



git reset --soft HEAD~1
git reset <file>
git restore --staged file_to_be_unstaged.txt



git config [--global] user.name "NAME HERE"
git config [--global] user.email "email@domain.org"



fast forward merge:
git checkout [branch we will merge into]
git merge [previous branch] (attempting a fast forward merger is the default)
optional: git branch -d [previous branch]



merge commit:
git checkout [branch we will merge into]
git merge [previous branch] [--no-ff (force a merge commit)]

^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
(git will attempt merge commit if not fast-forwardable)
optional: git branch -d [previous branch]
